# Reserved for Queue consumer jobs (Phase 5).
#
# Each job handler processes messages from the dentalaios-jobs queue.
# Workers export a `queue` handler with shape:
#   { queue: (batch, env, ctx) => Promise<void> }
#
# Suggested jobs (Phase 5):
# - sync-lark.task.ts      → retry failed Lark task creation
# - sync-lark.calendar.ts  → retry failed Lark calendar event creation
# - generate-pdf.ts        → async PDF generation for large plans
# - notify-overdue.ts      → cron-style reminder for unpaid treatments